title: vistara 13 L Tower Air Cooler(White, Nexa Tower Air Cooler 13 Liters Tower Air Cooler with Ice Chamber)
description: Vistara air coolers work on evaporative air technology which is the most natural way of cooling. With no gaseous refrigerants used in vistara air coolers and low power consumption, it is the most healthy and energy efficient way of getting cool air comfort. Unlike air conditioners, which circulates trapped air inside the room, vistara air coolers keeps drawing fresh air through open doors and windows and gives continuous flow of cool and fresh air. Our air cooler range is a ready to use heavy duty range designed for large cooling volumes. Evaporative air cooling is the most efficient and environment-friendly cooling technology which works on the principle of heat absorption by water evaporation. A pump circulates water from the tank on to a cooling pad making it wet. The blower draws hot air from outside the unit and forces it through the moistened pad. As the air passes through the wet pad it gets cooled by evaporation. The blower and motor are sized and designed to deliver the appropriate airflow.

With no gaseous refrigerants used in vistara air coolers and low power consumption, it is the most healthy and energy efficient way of getting cool air comfort. Unlike air conditioners, which circulates trapped air inside the room, vistara air coolers keeps drawing fresh air through open doors and windows and gives continuous flow of cool and fresh air. Our air cooler range is a ready to use heavy duty range designed for large cooling volumes. Evaporative air cooling is the most efficient and environment-friendly cooling technology which works on the principle of heat absorption by water evaporation. A pump circulates water from the tank on to a cooling pad making it wet. The blower draws hot air from outside the unit and forces it through the moistened pad. As the air passes through the wet pad it gets cooled by evaporation. The blower and motor are sized and designed to deliver the appropriate airflow. title: THE. 55 L Room/Personal Air Cooler(Multicolor, Magic Windmill Cube Desert Air Cooler)
description: THE. Magic Windmill Cube Energy Efficient, Indoor & Semi-Outdoor Portable Air coolers that come with A world of features Magic air coolers gives instant relief from the scorching heat by delivering strong gush of naturally cooled air even in peak summer. Every cooler is made with highest quality components to give robust & outstanding performance under extreme weather conditions while superior aesthetics tastefully add up to the surrounding ambience. Magic coolers work on evaporative air technology which is the most natural way of cooling. Warm air is drawn inside the cooler through cooling pads on which water is continuously dripped evenly. The water drops take the heat of air and evaporates thereby cooling the air inside the cooler. Cool air is then blown out of the cooler by powerful blower or fan to give cool air comfort. No gaseous refrigerants are used in Magic air coolers and with low power consumption, it is the healthiest and energy efficient way of getting cool air. Unlike, air conditioner which circulates trapped air inside the room, Magic air coolers keeps drawing fresh air through open windows and doors and gives continuous flow of cool and fresh air.

title: vistara 4 L Room/Personal Air Cooler(Red, White, AC/DC Inverter Portable Battery Operated Cooler USB port LED Light supports inbuilt rechargeable battery)
description: Vistara Alto Cooler works with & without electricity. 100% ABS body. USB port for mobile charger & LED light. Honeycomb pad for extra cooling, Supports (12V-6A) rechargeable battery (Not included). Blower fan. Includes LED light. Works upto 3-4 hours on battery power backup. Ultra portable - table top. Supports AC/DC power. This portable cooler is Ideal for Indian summer, as it can work with car battery and run without electricity. It can be used for charging mobile phone with its USB port and included USB LED light for emergency. Vistara air coolers work on evaporative air technology which is the most natural way of cooling. With no gaseous refrigerants used in vistara air coolers and low power consumption, it is the most healthy and energy efficient way of getting cool air comfort. Unlike air conditioners, which circulates trapped air inside the room, vistara air coolers keeps drawing fresh air through open doors and windows and gives continuous flow of cool and fresh air. Our air cooler range is a ready to use heavy duty range designed for large cooling volumes. Evaporative air cooling is the most efficient and environment-friendly cooling technology which works on the principle of heat absorption by water evaporation. A pump circulates water from the tank on to a cooling pad making it wet. The blower draws hot air from outside the unit and forces it through the moistened pad. As the air passes through the wet pad it gets cooled by evaporation. The blower and motor are sized and designed to deliver the appropriate airflow.

description: Bring home the Symphony Sumo Jr-G 45L and get ready to be thrilled with its performance. As suggested by its name, the size, design, performance, strength of the sumo coolers are inspired by the sumo wrestlers. The desert air cooler is equipped with dial knob controls that help you operate the fan speed, cooling, and swing mode easily. It also has sturdy castor wheels that ensure trouble-free mobility from one place to another. Running other air conditioners all day long can cost a lot of money and take up so much space! Some of them even have to vent out a window, making it very inconvenient. Arctic Air sleek compact design fits nicely on your desk, nightstand or coffee table – wherever you need it! It’s great for dens, reading nooks, work, dorm rooms, offices, home offices, campers, work spaces, benches, basements, garages and more! It’s lightweight & even convenient for travel! Great for outdoors too! It’s not just safe to use but energy efficient !This personal space air cooler actually cools the air around you, where you need it most, while using the size and power consumption of a small fan!

description: he powerful, compact personal air cooler that pulls warm air from the room through its evaporative water filter to fill any space with cool, clean comfortable air! Arctic Air cools, humidifies, and purifies for better air! Simply fill with water, plug it into any standard wall outlet or USB port and enjoy! Mini Portable Air cools runs up to 8 hours per fill! Arctic Air is an evaporative air cooler that allows you to create your own personal climate! The whisper-quiet fan and soothing night light make it perfect to use throughout the night for a comfortable sleep! Compact and lightweight, not taking too much space, powered by a USB cable, easy to carry to the necessary places, suitable for offices, home, kitchens, bedrooms, and even convenient for travel, great for outdoors. Evaporating air cooler-it sucks in hot air through the back and then passes that hot air through a moisture chamber. As the air comes out the other side, it evaporates and thereby dissipates the heat, leaving cool air to blow about the room for Maximum Comfort Regular fans just move warm air around, while air conditioning units are big and bulky, expensive to buy and make a lot of noise, and dry the air out! Arctic Air cools and humidifies the air by simply using water evaporation from a quiet, energy-efficient fan! Because Arctic Air just uses water there are no nasty ozone-destroying chemical coolants to worry about either. Now you can have the best of both worlds and get cooler, moist air without the expense and drawbacks of air conditioning.
